entries.journal_entry_description: A freighter has gone missing. Nova Orion Industries wants you to find out what happened.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Journey to Dantooine space to find the missing freighter.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Journey to Lok space to find the missing freighter.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Journey to Yavin 4 space to find the missing freighter.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Journey to Dathomir space to find the missing freighter.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: You have successfully rescued the freighter. Return and report your experience.
